{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Who can repair a Galaxy washing machine near me?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"&lt;p&gt;If you&apos;re searching for Galaxy washer repair near you, Sears Home Services offers certified technicians in most areas across the U.S. Our experts are trained to diagnose and fix all Galaxy washer models, including front-load, top-load, and washer/dryer combos. Same-day or next-day appointments are often available, and service can be booked online or by phone for your convenience.&lt;/p&gt;"}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What are common problems with Galaxy washers that Sears can fix?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"&lt;p&gt;Sears Home Services repairs a wide range of Galaxy washer issues, including:&lt;/p&gt;
